\c 42
\s Abafowabo bakaJosefa baya eGibithe
\p
\v 1 UJakobe esebonile ukuthi kukhona amabele eGibithe\x + Seb. 7.11,12.\x*, uJakobe wathi emadodaneni akhe: Kungani likhangelana?
\v 2 Wathi futhi: Khangelani, sengizwile ukuthi kukhona amabele eGibithe; yehlani liye khona, lisithengele khona, ukuze siphile, singafi\x + 43.8.\x*.
\v 3 Abafowabo bakaJosefa abalitshumi basebesehla ukuthenga amabele eGibithe.
\v 4 Kodwa uBenjamini\x + 35.18.\x*, umfowabo kaJosefa, uJakobe kamthumanga labafowabo, ngoba wathi: Hlezi ehlelwe yingozi\x + 42.38.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Amadodana-ke kaIsrayeli afika ukuthenga phakathi kwababesiza, ngoba indlala yayikhona elizweni leKhanani.
\v 6 UJosefa-ke wayengumbusi phezu kwelizwe\x + 41.41.\x*; wathengisela abantu bonke belizwe; bafika-ke abafowabo bakaJosefa, bamkhothamela ngobuso emhlabathini\x + 37.7,9,10.\x*.
\v 7 UJosefa esebabonile abafowabo, wabazi, kodwa wazitshaya owemzini kubo, wakhuluma labo izinto ezilukhuni wathi kubo: Livela ngaphi? Bathi: Elizweni leKhanani, ukuthenga ukudla.
\v 8 UJosefa-ke wabazi abafowabo, kodwa bona kabamazanga.
\v 9 UJosefa wasekhumbula amaphupho awaphupha ngabo\x + 37.5,9.\x*, wathi kibo: Lizinhloli\x + Dute. 1.24. Josh. 14.7.\x*, ukuzabona ubunqunu belizwe lizile.
\v 10 Basebesithi kuye: Hatshi, nkosi yami; kodwa inceku zakho zize ukuthenga ukudla.
\v 11 Thina sonke singamadodana andodanye; singabaqotho, inceku zakho kazisizo inhloli.
\v 12 Wasesithi kubo: Hatshi, kodwa ukuzabona ubunqunu belizwe lizile.
\v 13 Basebesithi: Thina, izinceku zakho, siyizelamani ezilitshumi lambili, amadodana andodanye elizweni leKhanani; khangela-ke, icinathunjana likubaba lamuhla, enye kayi\add se\add*kho\x + 37.30.\x*.
\v 14 UJosefa wasesithi kubo: Yikho lokho engikutsho kini, ukuthi: Lizinhloli.
\v 15 Kulokhu lizahlolwa; \add nge\add*mpilo kaFaro\x + 1 Sam. 1.26; 17.55.\x*! kalisoze liphume lapha, ngaphandle kokuthi kufike umfowenu olicinathunjana lapha.
\v 16 Thumani omunye wenu, amlande umfowenu; kodwa lina lizabotshwa, ukuze kuhlolwe amazwi enu, ukuthi iqiniso likini yini; kodwa uba hatshi, impilo kaFaro! lizinhloli.
\v 17 Wasebafaka\f + \fk wabafaka: \fl Heb. \fq wababuthela.\f* esitokisini insuku ezintathu.
\v 18 UJosefa wasesithi kubo ngosuku lwesithathu: Yenzani lokhu ukuze liphile. Ngiyamesaba uNkulunkulu\x + Levi 25.43. Neh. 5.15.\x*.
\v 19 Uba lingabaqotho, kabotshwe omunye wabafowenu endlini yokulondolozwa kwenu, kodwa lina hambani, libuyele lamabele endlala ezindlu zenu,
\v 20 lilethe umnawenu olicinathunjana kimi\x + 42.34; 43.5; 44.23.\x*; khona amazwi enu ezaqiniswa, ukuze lingafi. Basebesenza njalo.
\p
\v 21 Basebekhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Isibili silecala ngomfowethu, ngoba sabona usizi lomphefumulo wakhe, nxa wasincenga, kodwa kasilalelanga; ngenxa yalokho sehlelwe yikuhlupheka lokhu\x + Jobe 36.8,9.\x*.
\v 22 URubeni wasebaphendula wathi: Kangitshongo yini ukuthi: Lingoni kumfana\x + 37.21.\x*? Kodwa kalilalelanga. Ngakho legazi lakhe, khangelani, liyabizwa\x + 9.5. 2 Lan. 24.22. Hlab. 9.12. Luka 11.50,51.\x*.
\v 23 Njalo bona babengazi ukuthi uJosefa uyezwa, ngoba kwakulomtoliki\x + Jobe 33.23.\x* phakathi kwabo.
\v 24 Njalo wabafulathela, wakhala inyembezi; wasetshibilikela kubo, wakhuluma kubo; wasethatha uSimeyoni kubo, wambopha phambi kwamehlo abo.
\p
\v 25 UJosefa waselaya ukuthi bagcwalise amasaka abo ngamabele, lokuthi babuyisele imali yabo, ngulowo lalowo esakeni lakhe, lokuthi babanike umphako wendlela; basebesenza njalo kubo.
\v 26 Basebesethwesa obabhemi babo amabele abo, basuka lapho.
\v 27 Kwathi omunye evula isaka lakhe\x + 42.35; 43.21.\x* ukuze anike ubabhemi wakhe ukudla endlini yezihambi\x + 43.21. Eks. 4.24.\x*, wabona imali yakhe, ngoba khangela, yayisemlonyeni wesaka lakhe.
\v 28 Wasesithi kubafowabo: Imali yami ibuyiselwe; futhi khangelani, isesakeni lami. Inhliziyo yabo yasisehluleka\f + \fk zasehluleka: \fl Heb. \fq yaphuma.\f*, bathuthumela, omunye komunye besithi: Kuyini lokhu uNkulunkulu akwenze kithi?
\p
\v 29 Basebebuyela kuJakobe uyise elizweni leKhanani, bamazisa konke abahlangene lakho, besithi:
\v 30 Indoda, umbusi walelolizwe, wasihalada, wasithatha njengenhloli zelizwe.
\v 31 Kodwa sathi kuye: Singabaqotho; kasisizo izinhloli;
\v 32 sasiyizelamani ezilitshumi lambili, amadodana kababa; enye kayi\add se\add*kho\x + 37.30.\x*, lecinathunjana lamuhla likubaba elizweni leKhanani.
\v 33 Lendoda, umbusi welizwe, wathi kithi: Ngalokhu ngizakwazi ukuthi lingabaqotho; tshiyani omunye wabafowenu kimi\x + 42.5,19,20.\x*, lithathele indlala yezindlu zenu\x + 42.19.\x*, lihambe,
\v 34 lilethe umnawenu olicinathunjana kimi; khona ngizabona ukuthi kalisizo izinhloli kodwa lingabaqotho, ngilinike umfowenu, lithengiselane elizweni\x + 34.10,21.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Kwasekusithi sebethulula amasaka abo, khangela-ke, isikhwama semali salowo lalowo sisesakeni lakhe. Lapho bebona izikhwama zemali yabo, bona loyise, besaba.
\v 36 UJakobe uyise wasesithi kubo: Liyangemuka abantwana\x + 27.45; 43.14. Levi 26.22. 1 Sam. 15.33. 2 Sam. 17.8. Zaga 17.12. Jer. 18.21. Hos. 13.8.\x*; uJosefa ka\add se\add*kho loSimeyoni kakho, loBenjamini lizamthatha; zonke lezizinto zimelane lami.
\v 37 URubeni wasekhuluma kuyise esithi: Bulala ababili kumadodana ami\x + 46.9.\x*, uba ngingambuyisi kuwe; mnikele esandleni sami, futhi mina ngizambuyisa kuwe.
\v 38 Kodwa wathi: Indodana yami kayiyikwehla lani, ngoba umfowabo ufile\x + 42.13,32,36.\x*, futhi yena usele yedwa; uba esehlelwa yingozi endleleni elihamba kuyo\x + 42.4; 44.29.\x*, lizakwehlisela engcwabeni izimvu zami ngosizi\x + 37.35; 44.31.\x*.
